  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of MEM 1003 Versus Placebo in Patients With Mild to Moderate Alzheimer's Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Study to Evaluate Safety and Efficacy of MEM 1003 in Patients With Mild to Moderate Alzheimer's Disease</official_title>
  <sponsors>
